{"tid":1275381,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【林鄭政權涉嫌找來演員衝擊立法會大樓並嫁禍示威者】","createTime":"2019-07-01T19:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T19:41:35.000Z","uid":270077,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9c296c64307cf672d3b4314116aa3dd47254dce2","tid":1275381,"uid":270077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:32:07.000Z","msg":"經過一小時衝擊，玻璃門嚴重破裂， 帶頭衝擊的人突然離開前線走入人群，其他人接力推鐵籠車，最後整架撞入大樓。（相信此乃林鄭政權派來衝擊嫁禍示威者的演員）<br />\n<br />\n示威者之後斷斷續續衝擊，最終玻璃門斷開，但示威者無衝入去，而是暫時向後退。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=353797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D353797&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9CyIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=c5a4ccf7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D353797&h=0f4b28c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=353797</a>"},{"pid":"192e8d8230e6dc1663b353c89291e9789165dfb0","tid":1275381,"uid":81698,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:34:40.000Z","msg":"P牌仔88"},{"pid":"809478c48390f4fc66bb04bb071737451199c924","tid":1275381,"uid":270077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:36:44.000Z","msg":"在此強烈譴責林鄭政權涉嫌設局誘使示威者衝擊立法會大樓，另外警方刻意撤退縱容示威者任意進入立法會大樓進行破壞，企圖從而扭轉民意，為建制派選舉爭取民意支持，從而繼續控制區議會及立法會。"},{"pid":"659ed92b71e02065cacbda2880a5681f7b8efa88","tid":1275381,"uid":224402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:37:31.000Z","msg":"係咪又警黑合作？"},{"pid":"0bbff3d13a4b2d78e3cfddea7283e401e76689d9","tid":1275381,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:37:38.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"df69c6ccbc798d6c84f3e091c79521eeb546e61b","tid":1275381,"uid":167878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:38:32.000Z","msg":"p牌 block"},{"pid":"6ac2d9651ec2e1c9ac42a38b6985c723be76eeab","tid":127